<DOCHDR>
http://www.eren.doe.gov:80/hydrogen/hscan.htm 205.168.79.27 19970115051419 text/html 3399
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Wed, 15 Jan 1997 05:14:23 GMT
