<DOCHDR>
http://www.eren.doe.gov:80/hydrogen/carbon.htm 205.168.79.27 19970115052651 text/html 2856
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Wed, 15 Jan 1997 05:26:57 GMT
Server: NCSA/1.5
