studies. A short <a href="current.htm">summary</a> and the text of the <a 
href="rfptoc.htm">solicitation</a> are available. Persons interested in 
responding to the solicitation are strongly encouraged to request a copy 
of the solicitation from the Point of Contact in order to receive any 
updates or revisions that may occur.
