<H2> Process Simulation</H2>
<p>
Detailed modeling of a process can provide insight into research needs. 
The Hydrogen Program uses process simulation techniques to assist 
researchers needs, particularly in identifying areas for improvement. 
Select a technical summary for more information:
<p>
<ul><b>
<li><a href="techeco.htm">Technical and Economic Analysis of Renewable 
Hydrogen Production</a><br><i>National Renewable Energy Laboratory</i><p>

<li><a href="modeling.htm">Modeling Biomass Pyrolysis for Hydrogen 
Production</a><br><i>Jet Propulsion Laboratory, California Institute of 
Technology</i></b>
</li></li></ul>
