<DOCNO>WT02-B17-92</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA060-000333-B044-240</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.eren.doe.gov:80/hydrogen/duelbed.htm 205.168.79.27 19970115052901 text/html 3817
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Wed, 15 Jan 1997 05:28:59 GMT
Server: NCSA/1.5
