<DOCHDR>
http://www.eren.doe.gov:80/Harvest/brokers/queryhelp.html 205.168.79.27 19970115010534 text/html 8884
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Wed, 15 Jan 1997 01:05:16 GMT
