<DOCNO>WT02-B17-356</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA083-000589-B024-142</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.conservation.org:80/web/fieldact/regions/botswana.htm 38.253.200.3 19970216023652 text/html 4126
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.13
