<DOCOLDNO>IA083-000589-B024-219</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.conservation.org:80/web/fieldact/regions/indonesi.htm 38.253.200.3 19970216023738 text/html 5158
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.13
Date: Sunday, 16-Feb-97 02:42:35 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 31-Oct-96 16:38:56 GMT
Content-length: 4973
